# flan-t5-kelm-tekgen-kg-w-context-small-finetuned

Google's Flan T5 model ([flan-t5-small](https://huggingface.co/google/flan-t5-small)) finetuned over the KELM TEKGEN corpus using the prompting method used for [KGT-5](https://huggingface.co/spaces/apoorvumang/kgt5) with additional context supplied alongside the prompts.
